<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 09:15:47 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国节俭的年轻人加速储蓄，增加经济风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-frugal-young-adults-accelerate-saving-raising-economic-risks-2025-01-20/</link><description>随着Z世代回避政府关于花钱、花钱、花钱和加倍储蓄的号召，中国在新冠疫情造成的经济混乱期间开始并在房地产市场危机中深化的节俭趋势正在加剧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 09:02:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-frugal-young-adults-accelerate-saving-raising-economic-risks-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国称缅甸军方与少数民族武装组织同意停火</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-military-minority-armed-group-agree-ceasefire-china-says-2025-01-20/</link><description>中国外交部表示，缅甸军方和缅甸民族民主联盟军（MNDAA）签署了一项正式停火协议，该协议于周六开始，两国边境附近的战斗停止。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 08:50:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-military-minority-armed-group-agree-ceasefire-china-says-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>英国拉米称美国审查查戈斯群岛协议是“正确的”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uks-lammy-says-it-is-right-us-reviews-chagos-islands-deal-2025-01-20/</link><description>英国外交大臣戴维·拉米表示，美国新政府有机会审查与毛里求斯就美英在印度洋军事基地的未来达成的协议，这是正确的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 08:45:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uks-lammy-says-it-is-right-us-reviews-chagos-islands-deal-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普提议美国拥有 TikTok 50% 所有权后，中国敦促独立商业决策</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-urges-independent-business-decision-making-after-trump-proposes-50-us-2025-01-20/</link><description>中国外交部周一表示，企业应“独立决定”其运营和交易事宜，回应有关美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普提议美国持有 TikTok 50% 股权的问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 07:42:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-urges-independent-business-decision-making-after-trump-proposes-50-us-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>报告称中国商飞计划今年将C919喷气式飞机产能提升至50架</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-comac-aims-lift-c919-jet-production-capacity-50-this-year-report-says-2025-01-20/</link><description>中国商飞公司一位高管对上海政府支持的一家媒体表示，中国商飞公司计划今年将其国产 C919 单通道飞机的产能提高到 50 架。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 07:21:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-comac-aims-lift-c919-jet-production-capacity-50-this-year-report-says-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国投资者涌入桥水基金，关注特朗普回归</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-pile-into-bridgewater-style-funds-eyeing-trump-return-2025-01-20/</link><description>中国对冲基金经理正在竞相推出以桥水基金流行的“全天候”策略为蓝本的产品，以满足投资者对唐纳德·特朗普第二任美国总统期间预期波动的缓冲需求。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 07:16:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-pile-into-bridgewater-style-funds-eyeing-trump-return-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>2024年中国从主要供应国俄罗斯的原油进口量再创新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-crude-oil-imports-top-supplier-russia-reach-new-high-2024-2025-01-20/</link><description>周一数据显示，2024年中国从最大供应国俄罗斯的原油进口量比2023年增长1%，创历史新高，而从沙特阿拉伯的采购量下降9%，因炼油商追逐打折的俄罗斯供应以应对利润疲软。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 06:19:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-crude-oil-imports-top-supplier-russia-reach-new-high-2024-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>台湾行政长官称反对派削减预算将削弱政府关键职能</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-premier-says-oppositions-budget-cuts-would-cripple-key-government-2025-01-20/</link><description>台湾总理周一表示，由于反对党提出大幅削减今年的预算，政府面临包括国家安全在内的日常运作危机，反对党称需要减少浪费。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 04:28:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-premier-says-oppositions-budget-cuts-would-cripple-key-government-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚外长称华盛顿四方会议展现了“铁一般”的承诺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-foreign-minister-says-quad-washington-shows-iron-clad-commitment-2025-01-20/</link><description>澳大利亚外交部长黄英贤在华盛顿会见了印度和日本外长，并表示邀请四方外长参加当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的就职典礼表明了对印太地区密切合作的“坚定承诺”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 03:44:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-foreign-minister-says-quad-washington-shows-iron-clad-commitment-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>保守派影响者在 TikTok 赞助的特朗普就职派对上庆祝</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/conservative-influencers-celebrate-tiktok-sponsored-trump-inauguration-party-2025-01-20/</link><description>在周日为即将上任的总统唐纳德·特朗普和他曾经试图禁止的视频共享平台举行的就职庆典上，参加派对的人们戴着 TikTok 耳罩和 MAGA 帽子。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 03:33:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/conservative-influencers-celebrate-tiktok-sponsored-trump-inauguration-party-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普重返白宫之际，中国既充满希望又紧张不安</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/china-vice-president-meets-with-elon-musk-ahead-trump-inauguration-2025-01-20/</link><description>随着唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫，中国官员和普通民众满怀希望，但又感到紧张，渴望避免重演他第一个任期内导致两个经济超级大国之间产生裂痕的残酷贸易战。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 03:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/china-vice-president-meets-with-elon-musk-ahead-trump-inauguration-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>碧桂园律师告诉法庭，预计二月份与债权人达成协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-expects-reach-terms-with-creditors-february-lawyer-tells-court-2025-01-20/</link><description>中国碧桂园的律师周一告诉香港一家法院，碧桂园预计下个月与债权人就 164 亿美元离岸债务重组达成协议，并于 4 月份申请法院批准这些条款。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 02:07:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-expects-reach-terms-with-creditors-february-lawyer-tells-court-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>东盟维持禁止缅甸将军参加峰会的决定，敦促在南海保持克制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-upholds-decision-bar-myanmar-generals-summits-urges-self-restraint-s-china-2025-01-20/</link><description>现任轮值主席国马来西亚周一表示，东南亚集团东盟各国外长在周末务虚会上维持了禁止缅甸执政将军参加峰会并将缅甸的参与限制在非政治层面的决定。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 01:41:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-upholds-decision-bar-myanmar-generals-summits-urges-self-restraint-s-china-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>随着特朗普第二任期的到来，美元下跌，股市上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2025-01-20/</link><description>周一，美元走低，股市谨慎乐观，投资者等待唐纳德·特朗普就任第二任总统的头几个小时内预期将发布的一系列政策公告，并关注日本在本周末加息。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 01:17:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2025-01-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国维持基准贷款利率不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-leaves-benchmark-lending-rates-unchanged-2025-01-20/</link><description>正如预期的那样，中国连续第三个月维持基准贷款利率不变，因为人民币贬值限制了北京的货币政策宽松力度。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 01:06:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-leaves-benchmark-lending-rates-unchanged-2025-01-20/</guid></item></channel></rss>